Introducing Rapper/Singer/Producer/Songwriter Chris "Phantom" Fields! Hailing From Brooklyn,NY Chris Fields Works At Unleashing His Pain, Love, Past & His Future Through His Music Whether Its Rapping, Singing Or Beat Making. With Over 170,000 Views On Worldstarhiphop ("Lord Knows" Freestyle) & The Release Of His Mixtape "Lasers & Love 2" Chris Continues To Work To Accomplish His Musical Goals. Currently Chris has completed his 5th studio CD King Of Everything" which features production from IAMNOBODI, Serious Beats, Talen Ted, Hippie Sabatoge and !llMind. Download is available via Hotnewhiphop.com!!!

I'm all about new sounds. Soulection and their T.S.O.T. (The Sound of Tomorrow) caught my ear and I haven't been the same since, so everyday I look forward to hearing more sounds from lots of different artists. Favorite artists at this time are KAYTRANADA, Evil Needle, Sango, Iamnobodi, LAKIM, MR. CAR/\\ACK, and Sam Gellaitry. Such amazing talent from these and more. Not just from the Soulection crew, but from all over the world.
